<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TCV26">
<l>āṇiṉōṭu peṇṇumāki yallavōṭu nallavā</l>
<l>yūṇoṭō cai yūṟumāki yoṉṟalāta māyaiyāyp</l>
<l>pūṇipēṇu māyaṉākip poyyiṉōṭu meyyumāyk</l>
<l>kāṇipēṇu māṇiyāykka rantuceṉṟa kaḷvaṉē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Becoming a woman, a man, neither, becoming the good one(s),</l>
<l>becoming the experience (of taste), the sound, and the sense of touch,</l>
<l>O wonderful [Lord] who is not [the cause for just] one thing!</l>
<l>Turning into a cowherd tending cattle, becoming the truth along with untruth,</l>
<l rend="indent">O Thief who went concealing Yourself as a dwarf who nurtured the land!</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
